Package com.ibm.di.connector.maximo.parsing

Provides classes for parsing and schema data handling.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EntryConverter
    This class consists exclusively of static methods that operate on or return Entry objects and DOM elements.
    MxConnXSDEcoreBuilder
    This class loads XSD files from HTTP servers using the HttpClient.
    Schema
    This class provides access to descriptive information about Maximo Objects Structures (MOS) based on its XML Schema Descriptor (XSD), which is generated by the Maximo Object Structure Application.
    SchemaConfiguration
    Configuration parameters required by schema objects.
    SchemaElement
    This class represents the structural elements that compose a schema object and contains all the metadata.
